main event: Two objects landed on highway 8 in Steelville, Missouri, and one was observed taking off again.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for one to two minutes,The objects were investigated by OSI,The report mentions possible interference from a scheduled air-to-ground exercise,The witness described a dome-shaped craft about 40 feet in diameter, which had portholes and rested on landing gear,TV activity was suspected of being related to the sighting.
sighted object: two objects, one of which was dome-shaped with portholes
witness description: Witnesses included civilians who reported seeing the objects land and take off.
